Image Token Cost Calculator Visualization. Formula: Tiles = ceil(W/512) * ceil(H/512). Tokens = 85 + Tiles * 170. Cost = Tokens * $2.50 / 1M. Examples as cards: 512x512 (1 tile = 255 tokens = $0.0006), 1024x1024 (4 tiles = 765 tokens = $0.0019), 1920x1080 (16 tiles = 2805 tokens = $0.007), 4K (64 tiles = 10965 tokens = $0.027). Cost scaling line chart. Annotation: "Preprocessing (crop, scale) saves cost without quality loss". German labels.